PALADIN

Paladins are the holy and unholy warriors of the Gods.  They hold similar 
views of honor as knights and cavaliers, and in fact many of them are just 
that.  They will fight solely and fiercely for there beliefs and causes of 
their God, with little thought for there own desires.  Paladins will use all 
but the most crude forms of armor and weaponry.  Those who have reached the 
highest statures are granted some minor spells by there God.  Paladins must 
possess decent physical attributes, and must also have an above average 
clarity of thinking as well as excellent social skills.

See also: PRACTICE
